data.description: Charming home in a quiet gated neighborhood. No flood insurance required here, but you get to sit on your front porch just across the street from the large Hide-A-Way Lake. Only a few doors down is a boat launch, too. As you walk into this spacious home with freshly painted walls and new flooring, you are greeted by open spaces and plenty of natural light. An open floor plan and cathedral ceilings allow for easy entertaining inside, while the covered patio area in the backyard is ideal for outdoor entertaining. The bedrooms feature large closets with plenty of storage space. With a detached double garage and a floored room above it, imagine what the possibilities could be if you lived here. Being sold As-Is. In addition, the home comes with a top-tier Elite home warranty to protect you after purchase!
